dc_title_s: City of Ypsilanti, Washtenaw County, Michigan; surveyed & drawn by C. S. Woodard.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. Cadastral map showing some land ownership and wards. Includes index of additions and 8 ill. 1 map: hand col.; 141x106 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
